column5: ...great content, this year! Please, see www.niagaraoutdoorshow.com ...thanx, Bill
We've had a table there the past 7 years. Not a bad local show.
Today is the day. Some good deals to be had.  Son and I will be there with Ugliboys Baits.
Have a good time and good luck at the show.

There is a much larger show just across the boarder that the wife and I might attend this afternoon.  http://www.the-fairgrounds.com/event/march-5-8-wny-sport-adn-travel-expo/  More info I just found.....  http://www.eriepromotions.com/sport/default.aspx
